title: Leaving Netflix is Killing The Office
description:
This video is brought to you by World Anvil. Use code "MIDNIGHT" to get 40% off the annual membership at https://www.worldanvil.com/?c=midnight
The Office left Netflix for Peacock in 2021, so how has that worked out? In this video I go over the legacy of The Office and how it was impacted by the streaming service move.
